  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Vildagliptin Compared to Metformin in Drug Naive Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Vildagliptin Compared to Metformin in Drug Naive Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Novartis Pharmaceuticals</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Novartis</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the safety and effectiveness of vildagliptin, an
      unapproved drug, compared to metformin in lowering overall blood glucose levels in people
      with type 2 diabetes who have not been previously treated with drug therapy to lower their
      blood sugar.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
